        <abstract> 
<p>Thanks CD for sending him copy of <hi rend="italic">Variation</hi>.</p> 
            <p>Describes results of his brother’s [August Müller] experiments on effect of climate on maize.</p>
            <p>Like ancestors of horses, young tapir is also striped.</p>
        </abstract>
